<HL>
   Who's News:
   Terminal Data Corp.
</HL>
<DATE>
09/07/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
<CO>
   TERM WNEWS
</CO>
<IN>
OFFICE EQUIPMENT (OFF)
</IN>
<LP>
   TERMINAL DATA Corp. (Moorpark, Calif.) -- Jeffrey A.
Wilson, 41 years old, president of the Adaptive Information
Systems unit of Hitachi Ltd., was named president and chief
executive officer of this designer and maker of document
imaging systems, effective Sept. 17, succeeding David W. Krar
Hutton, who resigned in July but remained temporarily as
chief operating officer. Richard M. Drysdale, chairman since
April, has been acting chief executive.
</LP>
