<IN>
RECREATION, ENTERTAINMENT, TOYS, MOVIES, PHOTOGRAPHY, SPORTS (REC)
</IN>
<LP>
   Polaroid Corp., Cambridge, Mass., said it agreed with
SMPIC, a Chinese photographic equipment maker and a unit of
the Ministry of Light Industry, to create Polaroid of
Shanghai Ltd., which will make and sell instant cameras in
China.
   The new company, which also will package film, will
initially have 130 employees.
</LP>
